node.text: Join DeVonn Francis and Joel Moore as they show you how to throw a fun Pride party this year through cooking, music, and decor, while chatting about fun places to go to in the NYC area. This event, along with the sales of the #LimitedEdition Pride watch will benefit the @trevorproject #PrideOnFossil
